'''Jess Lackaff''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed [[Hepmaga MiOrd]] and the [[Remplish]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the 16 years and older category. She was 27 at the time her entry was published.

